                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 198.) On the 8th I took the prisoner, and in his fob-pocket I found these two bills—I said "Where is the money?" he said he had the money and spent it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
